OL,3,CMinisters seek public's views on
OL,4,Ccouncil carve-up
OL,6,FControversial plans to cut the number
OL,7,Fof local authorities in the south and
OL,8,Freplace them with so-called "mega
OL,9,Fcouncils" are to be put to a public
OL,10,Fconsultation.
OL,12,FThe government wants to end separate
OL,13,Fcounty and district councils in areas
OL,14,Fwhere they still exist.
OL,16,FExisting councils were invited to
OL,17,Fsubmit proposals for moving from the
OL,18,Ftwo-tier system to unitary authorities
OL,19,Fbut many failed to reach agreement.
