OL,3,CMinisters seek public's views on
OL,4,Ccouncil carve-up
OL,6,FConsultations will now be held on
OL,7,Fvarious different proposals for how
OL,8,Fthe new council boundaries might look
OL,9,Fin Essex, Sussex and Hampshire.
OL,11,FIn Sussex, four rival options remain
OL,12,Fon the table, which would see the
OL,13,Fnumber of councils cut from 15 to
OL,14,Feither three, four or five ` in
OL,15,Fvarious configurations.
OL,17,FEast Sussex and West Sussex county
OL,18,Fcouncils each want to become unitary
OL,19,Fauthorities on their existing
OL,20,Fgeographical boundaries.
