OL,3,CMinisters seek public's views on
OL,4,Ccouncil carve-up
OL,6,FThere is an alternative proposal from
OL,7,Fthe district and borough councils in
OL,8,FWest Sussex for two unitary councils
OL,9,Fin that county.
OL,11,FThere is also another option from
OL,12,FBrighton and Hove City Council for
OL,13,Ffive new unitary councils across the
OL,14,Fentire historic county of Sussex.
OL,16,FIn Hampshire, four different options
OL,17,Ffor a new council map remain under
OL,18,Fconsideration by the government. All
OL,19,Fkeep a separate unitary council for
OL,20,Fthe Isle of Wight.
