OL,3,CMinisters seek public's views on
OL,4,Ccouncil carve-up
OL,6,FHampshire County Council and East
OL,7,FHampshire District Council favour
OL,8,Fmoving from 15 councils to four.
OL,10,FBut the other city, borough and
OL,11,Fdistrict councils disagree and have
OL,12,Fsubmitted three other competing
OL,13,Fproposals which each suggest a five
OL,14,Funitary model, but along different
OL,15,Fboundaries.
OL,17,FIn Essex, four options remain under
OL,18,Fconsideration for moving from 15
OL,19,Fcouncils to three, four or five.
