OL,3,CMinisters seek public's views on
OL,4,Ccouncil carve-up
OL,6,F"There's no independent evidence that
OL,7,Fmega councils are better performing or
OL,8,Fmore financially resilient ` smaller
OL,9,Funitary councils often deliver more
OL,10,Feffective services and are every bit
OL,11,Fas effective at driving growth and
OL,12,Fgetting homes built," the DCN added.
OL,14,FA recent ITV News Meridian
OL,15,Finvestigation found that councils in
OL,16,Fthe South had already budgeted #12
OL,17,Fmillion over two years for local
OL,18,Fgovernment reorganisation.
